# Apex is canonical; redirect www → apex (301).
https://www.lexitap.app/* https://lexitap.app/:splat 301

# Friendly aliases. NOTE: Cloudflare Pages' built-in pretty-URL feature already
# serves /privacy from privacy.html and 308s /privacy.html → /privacy. Aliases
# must therefore target EXTENSIONLESS paths — pointing one at a .html target
# creates an infinite 301↔308 loop (bit us: privacy/terms were unreachable).
/privacy-policy  /privacy  301
/account-deletion  /delete-account  301
